en:
In Paris,
Published by the Widow Boudot, at the Sign of the Golden Sun;
Etienne Ganeau, at the Arms of Dombes;
Claude Robustel, at the Sign of Saint John;
and Laurent Rondet, at the Sign of the Compass;
Rue Saint-Jacques, near the Fountain of Saint-Séverin.

1716.
With the King’s Approval and Privilege.
